# mscx-utils

Shared MuseScore `.mscz` / `.mscx` utilities used by **musescore-part-formatter** and **musescore-score-diff**.

## `mscx_utils.archive`

- `unpack_mscz_to_tempdir` — extract to a temp dir (optional in-place repack)
- `extract_mscz` / `extract_mscz_main_mscx` — extract archives and locate the main score
- `pick_main_mscx_arc_from_namelist`, `mscx_path_from_extract_dir`, `is_excerpt_mscx_arc`
- `mscx_arcnames`, `partition_mscx_arcs` — inspect archive layout
- `write_mscz_from_dir`, `remove_excerpts_from_mscz_dir` — write or trim extracted trees

## `mscx_utils.score_xml`

- `load_score_element` — parse a `.mscx` and return its `<Score>` element
